00:39:43,105 --> 00:39:45,232
It's strange, isn't it?

561
00:39:46,375 --> 00:39:50,937
But for me,
what's really strange about this is, um...

562
00:39:52,147 --> 00:39:57,585
remembering writing these things,
you know, which was so little -

563
00:39:57,653 --> 00:40:02,955
little guitar, little old piano, bit of paper
and a pencil, the back of an envelope.

564
00:40:03,025 --> 00:40:05,289
You know,
"Sergeant Pepper" or something.

565
00:40:05,394 --> 00:40:09,524
So it was such a little process,
and look what's happened to it.

566
00:40:09,631 --> 00:40:11,622
(George Martin) It is amazing.

