00:40:18,874 --> 00:40:24,176
(George Martin) It's very difficult
to escape this heritage that we have.

568
00:40:25,180 --> 00:40:30,584
I've been having memories brought back
every day of my life.

569
00:40:31,587 --> 00:40:35,683
There will be a little knot of Beatle fans
somewhere who says:

570
00:40:35,791 --> 00:40:40,160
"They shouldn't do that. They should
leave the masters as we know them."

571
00:40:40,229 --> 00:40:44,097
But we're embarking on
a new direction here.

