00:42:13,655 --> 00:42:17,785
It seemed like it could be now,
in a way.

599
00:42:17,860 --> 00:42:21,421
I thought they could have
made me a bit taller.

600
00:42:21,496 --> 00:42:25,296
That's the only thing I thought,
"My God, can't I be taller now?"

601
00:42:25,400 --> 00:42:27,868
"Seeing as I'm a shadow."

602
00:42:29,805 --> 00:42:32,433
How did the guys
get together to do a tune right?

