00:43:15,817 --> 00:43:18,945
George Martin was like
the grown-up in the group.

616
00:43:19,021 --> 00:43:21,012
George was...

617
00:43:21,123 --> 00:43:24,559
We were like the kids.
In fact, they used to call us "the boys."

618
00:43:24,626 --> 00:43:27,754
That was the working title
of this show, wasn't it?

619
00:43:27,829 --> 00:43:30,992
And we always used to joke,
but we were, like...

620
00:43:31,066 --> 00:43:36,060
In the later years, we were, like, 28
