Somebody calls you,
you answer quite slowly

788
00:55:37,425 --> 00:55:39,985
A girl with kaleidoscope eyes

789
00:55:40,061 --> 00:55:44,896
(George Martin) I want you to fix me up
so that I can do one of those things.

790
00:55:44,999 --> 00:55:47,934
- You mean hang with harnesses?
- I could join her up there.

791
00:55:48,036 --> 00:55:50,664
- Well, no problem.
- (both laugh)

