833
00:59:27,722 --> 00:59:29,986
- (Champagne) I am, honestly.
- Great.

834
00:59:30,057 --> 00:59:32,958
Tell me what you were inspired about,
and the words.

835
00:59:33,027 --> 00:59:37,760
He's singing so well and I feel so sorry
for him because nothing's going on.

836
00:59:37,832 --> 00:59:40,892
It's just making it like...
Oh, "atmospheric" is the word.

837
00:59:41,002 --> 00:59:46,497
But it's not atmospheric.
Beatles' thing is power. Also...

838
00:59:46,574 --> 00:59:51,443
I have, you know, a lot of respect
for him, for having done this much.

839
00:59:51,512 --> 00:59:56,848
And of course we're all still saying, "Well,
could you just..." et cetera, et cetera.

840
00:59:56,951 --> 00:59:59,818
Olivia is going there and I'm going there

841
00:59:59,921 --> 01:00:05,359
because we are very protective
of our husbands' songs, you know.

842
